title: Projects
text:
Check out my projects!














Capstone





Capstone project modeling and predicting socioeconomic factors influencing premature deaths in the US for SURE 2024 At Carnegie Mellon University





Jul 1, 2024












EDA Project - SURE 2024





Through this project in the SURE program from Carnegie Mellon, my team and I were able to do a Exploratory Data Analysis in R to understand the relationship and patterns between Covid cases and deaths in PA during the year 2020 using cluster analysis, bivariate cheropleth map and overtime bar charts.





Jun 1, 2024












Empty Shelves - Final ANOP 330





Final Project from Predictive Analytics class (ANOP 330). Through this project I use machine learning in Python to test multiple models, such as decision tree, KNN, Logistic regression and random forest, to see which ones have the highest succeess rate when predicting the occurance of backorder, when a customer places an order for a product that is currently unavailable in inventory.





Nov 1, 2023












How Much Fun Are BucknellToys Delivering? - Midterm ANOP 270





Midterm project from Data Visualization class (ANOP 270). I explored the sales and profits in the store Bucknell Toys and other relevant patterns such as inventory, sales per week, top selling toys, etc.





Mar 1, 2023












The Power of Connection - Final ANOP 270





In my final project for my data visualization class I presented a dashboard made in Tableau about the relationship between internet accessibility and education, and how the access to internet influence human development per country between 1990 and 2020.
